# Patterns are matched against the workspace root. Nested workspaces need the
# ** prefix — a bare `dist` would only match /dist, not apps/*/dist.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.DS_Store
**/*.local
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
CONTINUITY.md
**/CONTINUITY.md
.claude/
.git
.github
**/.playwright-cli
output/playwright
.impeccable
